yourself presents and candy?

02:39.590 --> 02:40.870
That's crazy talk!

02:41.090 --> 02:44.020
I THINK what Spike
means to say is,

02:44.130 --> 02:46.950
Hearth's Warming is about
more than presents and candy.

02:47.190 --> 02:49.340
It's a time to spend
with friends and family

02:49.390 --> 02:51.260
when we celebrate a
very important day

02:51.300 --> 02:52.680
in Equestria's history.

02:52.870 --> 02:55.510
I think to most ponies,
it's just an excuse

02:55.560 --> 02:57.360
for silly songs and fun,

02:57.650 --> 03:00.370
not a day to remember
some old story.

03:02.250 --> 03:03.670
Maybe you just haven't
heard the right

03:03.730 --> 03:05.510
Hearth's Warming
Eve story yet.

03:06.020 --> 03:08.310
Earth ponies, pegasi
and unicorns sing songs

03:08.350 --> 03:10.690
around a hearth to fight
back an eternal winter

03:10.740 --> 03:12.470
caused by the
mythical Windigos?

03:12.590 --> 03:15.050
Every foal and fill
knows that story.

03:15.390 --> 03:18.280
Not THAT one. My
favorite holiday story.

03:18.490 --> 03:20.000
A Hearth's Warming Tale.

03:20.200 --> 03:22.000
Oooooo! I love that one!

03:24.710 --> 03:28.600
This is the story of a powerful
unicorn named Snowfall Frost

03:28.750 --> 03:30.570
who hated Hearth's
Warming Eve!

03:30.900 --> 03:33.580
It all began many moons
ago in Canterlot...

03:34.770 --> 03:37.920
Every home in Canterlot was
filled with Holiday spirit.

03:38.650 --> 03:40.550
Every home except one.

03:41.320 --> 03:43.670
It was said of Snowfall that
she was almost as studied

03:43.720 --> 03:44.930
as Starswirl the Bearded.

03:46.090 --> 03:49.650
Almost, since everypony knows
that Starswirl was an expert

03:49.690 --> 03:51.500
at everything from
transfiguration,

03:51.590 --> 03:53.960
Dimensional Calibration,
Teleportation--

03:54.300 --> 03:56.390
We get it.
Starswirl's awesome.

03:56.590 --> 04:00.610
Right. The point is, Snowfall
was also a powerful unicorn.

04:00.960 --> 04:02.670
She wanted to be perfect.

04:02.840 --> 04:05.200
Anything that got in the way
of that was a waste of time.

04:06.490 --> 04:07.330
Ugh!

04:10.150 --> 04:13.070
Well, that batch is
ruined. SNOWDASH!

04:13.520 --> 04:15.780
Snowdash was Snowfall's
loyal assistant.

04:16.420 --> 04:17.110
What do you need?

04:17.260 --> 04:18.570
Get this mess cleaned up.

04:18.860 --> 04:21.410
Those foolish ponies were
ringing those blasted bells

04:21.460 --> 04:24.070
outside the window and
I lost my concentration.

04:24.400 --> 04:26.080
Whoa. Ponies
actually enjoying

04:26.120 --> 04:29.130
Hearth's Warming Eve. Where
did they get that crazy idea?

04:29.420 --> 04:31.300
Today is nothing
to celebrate.

04:31.390 --> 04:33.260
Hearth's Warming
Eve is a menace,

04:33.620 --> 04:35.950
a dangerous day for
all of Equestria.

04:36.100 --> 04:38.280
Dangerous? It's awesome!

04:38.530 --> 04:40.980
It's the day we remember
how unicorns, pegasi,

04:41.040 --> 04:43.010
and earth ponies came
together in friendship

04:43.060 --> 04:44.880
to defeat the Windigos!

04:45.000 --> 04:47.230
That silly legend
is the problem!

04:47.540 --> 04:50.630
Telling everypony that
singing songs and being nice

04:50.670 --> 04:54.200
will solve anything? I've
spent years studying magic

04:54.280 --> 04:56.250
and that's not how it works.

04:56.590 --> 04:58.810
I think you might be
missing the point.

04:59.360 --> 05:03.140
Work hard, learn and use your
skills to better Equestria.

05:03.640 --> 05:05.460
THAT'S a worthy
goal for anypony.

05:06.560 --> 05:09.470
But by all means, if you
want to go home early,

05:09.590 --> 05:12.090
ignore all of the work you
have and spend the rest --

05:12.130 --> 05:13.250
SWEET!

05:14.230 --> 05:15.000
Ugh.

05:17.950 --> 05:20.250
I HATE Hearth's Warming Eve!

05:20.610 --> 05:22.670
All of Equestria
would be better off

05:22.710 --> 05:25.160
if we just skipped
the day all together.

