06:04.440 --> 06:07.310
<i> ♪ The greatest gift</i>
<i> that I give today ♪</i>

06:07.550 --> 06:10.810
<i> ♪ And everypony will</i>
<i> have to face it. ♪</i>

06:11.070 --> 06:17.920
<i> ♪ No more little games</i>
<i> for you to play ♪</i>

06:19.230 --> 06:23.060
<i> ♪ After you say goodbye</i>
<i> to the holiday. ♪</i>

06:26.600 --> 06:28.560
<i> ♪ Goodbye Hearth's Warming ♪</i>

06:28.620 --> 06:29.990
<i> ♪ You had a good run ♪</i>

06:30.070 --> 06:32.010
<i> ♪ Goodbye Hearth's Warming ♪</i>

06:32.060 --> 06:33.750
<i> ♪ It's over, you're done ♪</i>

06:33.980 --> 06:35.510
<i> ♪ Finally set free from ♪</i>

06:35.550 --> 06:37.330
<i> ♪ your forced celebrations ♪</i>

06:37.470 --> 06:38.780
<i> ♪ no need to reply ♪</i>

06:38.840 --> 06:40.860
<i> ♪ to your trite invitations ♪</i>

06:40.990 --> 06:44.060
<i> ♪ Calendars shorter</i>
<i> by a single day ♪</i>

06:44.130 --> 06:46.960
<i>♪ Is my magic up to the test? ♪</i>

06:47.480 --> 06:54.620
<i>♪ Time to see, I can't delay. ♪</i>

06:55.010 --> 06:57.810
<i> ♪ Say goodbye to the holiday ♪</i>

06:58.030 --> 07:01.330
<i> ♪ Prepare the spell,</i>
<i> no hesitation ♪</i>

07:01.710 --> 07:04.740
<i>♪ All memories shall fade away ♪</i>

07:05.090 --> 07:08.530
<i> ♪ See Equestria's</i>
<i> new transformation ♪</i>

