<i>♪ No more shall any ponies say ♪</i>

07:16.550 --> 07:18.020
<i> ♪ "Happy Hearth's Warming" ♪</i>

07:20.440 --> 07:27.170
<i> ♪ after today! ♪</i>

07:28.200 --> 07:34.550
<i> ♪ After today. ♪</i>

07:38.330 --> 07:41.740
Once the spell is cast, all of
Equestria will be better off.

07:42.090 --> 07:44.270
