to say is that everypony

08:04.670 --> 08:08.020
has their reasons for doing
things. Even Snowfall.

08:08.300 --> 08:10.200
And if I could
continue the story,

08:10.390 --> 08:12.180
we might just find
out what they are.

08:12.670 --> 08:13.590
Proceed.

08:14.300 --> 08:17.520
Snowfall was all set to cast
her spell that would erase

08:17.570 --> 08:19.500
Hearth's Warming
Eve for all time

08:19.790 --> 08:22.100
when a voice from the hearth
caught her attention.

08:22.250 --> 08:24.530
You SURE you wanna
go through with this?

08:24.740 --> 08:26.220
Who's there!

08:27.900 --> 08:31.100
The Spirit of Hearth's
Warmin' Past, that's who.

08:33.040 --> 08:35.130
And you and me have got
to have us a little chat.

08:35.450 --> 08:40.300
A spirit! I didn't cast any
spirit-summoning spell.

08:40.680 --> 08:42.250
What are you doing here?

08:42.500 --> 08:44.360
You don't think a spell
like that would get by

08:44.400 --> 08:46.320
without some powerful
forces noticing?

08:46.580 --> 08:48.920
You've got our attention,
Snowfall Frost

08:49.320 --> 08:51.430
and we've got some
pretty strong opinions

08:51.470 --> 08:52.760
on this spell of yours.

08:53.020 --> 08:53.590
We?

08:53.880 --> 08:57.290
They'll be along in a bit.
For now it's just you and me.

08:57.490 --> 08:59.690
Let's get a move on.
We got a ton to see

08:59.730 --> 09:01.070
and barely any time
to see it.

09:01.230 --> 09:03.190
I'm not going anywhere.

09:03.460 --> 09:06.760
