09:48.520 --> 09:52.510
<i> ♪ So let's take a little</i>
<i> trip down memory lane ♪</i>

09:52.630 --> 09:57.060
<i> ♪ And see just what</i>
<i> the past has to say. ♪</i>

09:58.540 --> 10:00.550
Awww, look how
cute you were.

10:00.610 --> 10:01.890
Looks like you're
not too upset it's

10:01.940 --> 10:03.490
Hearth's Warming Eve, either.

10:04.130 --> 10:08.370
<i> ♪ The seeds of the past,</i>
<i> they grow pretty fast ♪</i>

10:08.580 --> 10:12.710
<i> ♪ Just look at who</i>
<i> you were back then ♪</i>

10:12.970 --> 10:17.160
<i> ♪ The seeds as they grow,</i>
<i> look what they can show ♪</i>

10:17.370 --> 10:22.580
<i> ♪ Reveal the truth</i>
<i> time and again ♪</i>

10:28.630 --> 10:31.520
Just what do you think
you are doing, Snowfall?

10:31.640 --> 10:33.720
Decorating the classroom
for Hearth's Warming Eve,

10:33.830 --> 10:34.900
Professor Flintheart!

10:35.580 --> 10:39.100
You said you wanted to learn
to be a powerful unicorn,

10:39.160 --> 10:40.840
did you not?
I do!

10:41.110 --> 10:44.830
And what is the way that one
becomes a powerful unicorn?

10:45.930 --> 10:48.340
Work hard, learn
and use your skills

10:48.380 --> 10:49.730
to better Equestria.

10:52.420 --> 10:55.900
And how do these help
you to learn magic?

10:56.120 --> 10:59.200
I want to be strong enough to
stop Windigos and help ponies!

10:59.560 --> 11:02.770
That's just a story
we tell little ponies.

11:02.920 --> 11:05.400
Real magic takes
time to learn.

11:09.410 --> 11:10.450
It's your choice.

11:10.550 --> 11:13.590
Spend your time learning to
become a powerful unicorn,

11:13.810 --> 11:17.430
or play with your toys and
make nothing of yourself.

11:18.260 --> 11:22.520
<i> ♪ Then some distress,</i>
<i> words so careless ♪</i>

11:22.810 --> 11:26.340
<i> ♪ Standing there, you</i>
<i> don't know what to do ♪</i>

11:27.270 --> 11:31.400
