can't make it hurt less

11:31.610 --> 11:35.700
<i> ♪ So you go and change</i>
<i> your point of view. ♪</i>

11:36.600 --> 11:39.940
<i> ♪ And in that moment</i>
<i> though you didn't know it ♪</i>

11:40.990 --> 11:44.500
<i> ♪ Your defenses set up</i>
<i> walls you built to last ♪</i>

11:45.360 --> 11:48.960
<i> ♪ Leading to the pony</i>
<i> you've become today ♪</i>

11:49.100 --> 11:51.200
<i> ♪ And the spell you're</i>
<i> about to cast, ♪</i>

11:51.680 --> 11:54.820
<i>♪ it all comes from your past. ♪</i>

11:55.040 --> 11:59.460
<i> ♪ The seeds of the past'</i>
<i> we grow up so fast ♪</i>

11:59.620 --> 12:03.690
<i> ♪ Some hurts never go away ♪</i>

12:04.150 --> 12:08.270
<i> ♪ The seeds as they grow,</i>
<i> this we can't let go ♪</i>

12:08.340 --> 12:13.860
