12:18.570 --> 12:21.100
Spirit?
What am I supposed to--

12:24.390 --> 12:26.970
SNOWFALL FROST! IT IS I,

12:27.130 --> 12:30.330
THE SPIRIT OF HEARTH'S
WARMING PRESENTS!

12:31.430 --> 12:34.160
Um, don't you mean
present, like, the time?

12:34.290 --> 12:37.140
No. Toys, Hearth's Warming
dolls. Here! Want a cupcake?

12:38.110 --> 12:41.610
Fine. Presents. All of
the pointless things

12:41.660 --> 12:43.410
that ponies waste
their time on.

12:43.610 --> 12:46.650
Oh Snowfall. It's not what
the gift is that matters,

12:46.760 --> 12:48.570
it's what the gift MEANS!

12:49.010 --> 12:51.810
It doesn't mean anything.
It's just stuff.

12:51.930 --> 12:54.800
Exactly! Sometimes a
cupcake means I love you!

12:54.930 --> 12:56.750
Or a toy means Hi!
How ya doin?

12:56.880 --> 12:59.830
And sometimes a book means,
"Your mane looks AMAZING!"

12:59.950 --> 13:01.260
And sometimes a scarf means...

13:01.880 --> 13:04.060
well, a scarf usually
means you look cold.

13:04.270 --> 13:05.490
That one's easy.

13:06.010 --> 13:08.180
I don't understand
anything you're saying.

13:08.320 --> 13:10.800
Whoa, whoa!

13:10.920 --> 13:12.120
What's happening to you?

13:12.240 --> 13:15.560
My Spirit of Hearth's Warming
Presents-sense is going off!

13:15.770 --> 13:19.050
That means a song
is coming on!

