<i> ♪ Open up your heart;</i>
<i> it will surround you ♪</i>

13:33.050 --> 13:35.260
<i> ♪ In the magic of</i>
<i> Hearth's Warming Eve ♪</i>

13:35.810 --> 13:38.500
<i> ♪ The little things</i>
<i> that make it better ♪</i>

13:38.740 --> 13:40.960
<i> ♪ Little ponies</i>
<i> spreading cheer! ♪</i>

13:41.400 --> 13:44.120
<i>♪ Give a toy, a hug, a sweater ♪</i>

13:44.260 --> 13:46.350
<i>♪ Memories that last all year! ♪</i>

13:47.310 --> 13:49.920
<i> ♪ The present's always</i>
<i> filled with presents ♪</i>

13:50.090 --> 13:51.950
<i> ♪ Large, medium and small ♪</i>

13:52.330 --> 13:54.990
<i> ♪ Sometimes the most</i>
<i> important things ♪</i>

13:55.070 --> 13:57.410
<i> ♪ Aren't very big at all. ♪</i>

