<i> ♪ The cider's flowing,</i>
<i> this is living! ♪</i>

14:22.580 --> 14:24.570
<i> ♪ Come on and feel the beat! ♪</i>

14:25.160 --> 14:27.410
<i> ♪ Life is better</i>
<i> when you're givin' ♪</i>

14:28.060 --> 14:30.050
<i> ♪ Each time you do</i>
<i> it feels so sweet! ♪</i>

14:30.880 --> 14:33.520
<i> ♪ The present's always</i>
<i> filled with presents ♪</i>

14:33.580 --> 14:35.880
<i> ♪ So come on open your eyes ♪</i>

